column5: Hey Randy, ever fished the dams for pickeral and silver bass as a kid ?  Nuke
Oh god.... are we gonna have to hear about that again??  LOL ... just kidding Randy... let 'er go!!
Hey TJ, how long have you lived in Sturgeon ?  I was born, raised there, moved south for work at 21.  Maybe we have met ?  Nuke
Yeah TJ! You remember anyone in elementary school called Nuke?
Yes I did I lived  4 houses away from the dam... and I now like 2 blocks away...  fished there as a kid   and still do as an adult...  I might know you ...P.M me yer real name...

LOL.. I've been called PUKE a few times... hahaha  I've pretty much lived in Sturgeon my entire life, with a brief stay in the northern wilderness and New York..  I graduated high school at Northern in 82...
Is it true that your time at good old Northern was the hardest 10 years of your life?..........

TJ, if you graduated in '82, according to Dano, you started grade 9 in '72 !  Wow, your commitment and perseverance is overwhelming ! I graduated from Northern in '86, followed by 3 years at Cambrian.
LOL.. hey 10 years... its a record...  I also followed with 3 years at Cambrian and 2 at LSSU
